Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.51,0:00:04.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Someday... Yes, someday,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.68,0:00:06.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be walking down
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.10,0:00:13.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Episode 12: 'Friends and Love,\NLove and Cherry Blossoms'"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.10,0:00:13.05,Default,,0,0,0,,a spring path while looking up at the\Ncherry blossoms whether I want to or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.93,0:00:17.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a normal person.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.72,0:00:21.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have the ability to\Ntouch something I can't see,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.18,0:00:24.76,Default,,0,0,0,,and I can't involve myself in something\Nthat's not happening right in front of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.76,0:00:28.26,Default,,0,0,0,,What I'm scared of is while I'm not looking
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.26,0:00:32.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Shimamura will change into something different.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.72,0:00:40.26,Default,,0,0,0,,So I've made up my mind to spend\Nevery spare moment looking at Shimamura.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.76,0:00:45.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... Adachi.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.35,0:00:46.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.18,0:00:47.22,Default,,0,0,0,,--Pssh, pssh, pssh...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.22,0:00:48.39,Default,,0,0,0,,--Never mind.\N--Pssh, pssh, pssh...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.39,0:00:50.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Heyo, Shima!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.85,0:00:53.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Adachicchi is with you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.10,0:00:54.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Chicchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.60,0:00:58.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Hino and Nagafuji. It's been a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.05,0:00:59.97,Default,,0,0,0,,It sure has!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.39,0:01:05.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you change your shampoo, Nagafuji?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.43,0:01:08.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I spent the night\Nat Hino's place yesterday,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.97,0:01:11.18,Default,,0,0,0,,and took a bath there this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.18,0:01:12.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh...?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.89,0:01:16.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, you don't really\Nhave to talk about that now.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.89,0:01:19.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, it's our turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.01,0:01:20.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.10,0:01:22.68,Default,,0,0,0,,--Good luck out there.\N--Pssh, pssh, pssh, pssh, pssh...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.68,0:01:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Staying at someone's house...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.80,0:01:28.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Then using their bath and then\Nheading right to school...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.18,0:01:34.55,Default,,0,0,0,,C-Can I come over, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.55,0:01:35.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.68,0:01:37.14,Default,,0,0,0,,And spend the night.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.14,0:01:39.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, at Hino's place?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.80,0:01:45.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Your place, Shimamura.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.14,0:01:47.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.01,0:01:50.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.18,0:01:55.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, our bathtub's tiny.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.05,0:01:58.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't really care about the bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.14,0:02:02.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, do I? No, I think it does matter...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.51,0:02:12.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe it does matter...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.72,0:02:14.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Adachi?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.68,0:02:19.55,Default,,0,0,0,,That doesn't really matter...\NBut I want to spend the night!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.55,0:02:21.89,Default,,0,0,0,,But why?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.89,0:02:26.18,Default,,0,0,0,,B-Because I want to be\Ncloser to you, Shimamura...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.18,0:02:30.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Are we not close already? I had no idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.30,0:02:33.30,Default,,0,0,0,,No, we are, we are!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.30,0:02:38.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I think... But I want to be closer.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.64,0:02:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you get closer by spending the night, though?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.51,0:02:48.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.64,0:02:55.64,Default,,0,0,0,,A-Adachi?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.80,0:03:01.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Under the pretense of discussing\Nme spending the night,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.47,0:03:05.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I got to hang out with Shimamura\Nafter school... Wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.30,0:03:07.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Spending the night is awesome.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.26,0:03:08.89,Default,,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.89,0:03:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want to come over to\Nmy place this Saturday or Sunday?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.80,0:03:14.93,Default,,0,0,0,,T-Two days off...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.93,0:03:16.85,Default,,0,0,0,,And spending the night two nights...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.85,0:03:19.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You want to stay at my place that long?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.51,0:03:22.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Just so you know, my place isn't an inn.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.35,0:03:25.64,Default,,0,0,0,,What about work?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.64,0:03:29.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go to work... um, from your place.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.97,0:03:31.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hm.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.97,0:03:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Though there's probably going to be\None more when we get to my place.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.60,0:03:42.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not sure why, but it feels like\NI have two or three little sisters now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.10,0:03:45.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean me, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.26,0:03:54.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Her little sister... Shimamura Sakura.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.26,0:03:56.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like an alliteration.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.68,0:03:59.93,Default,,0,0,0,,We'd be even closer than friends then,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.93,0:04:02.47,Default,,0,0,0,,and that part's fine...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.64,0:04:08.10,Default,,0,0,0,,But then I think we'd get too close\Nand she'd notice me even less.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.10,0:04:09.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Change of underwear\NSocks 4? 5?\NFood: Bread & Instant ramen"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.43,0:04:12.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Change of underwear\NSocks 4? 5?\NFood: Bread & Instant ramen"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.43,0:04:12.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's all the stuff I'll need to buy...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.35,0:04:17.68,Default,,0,0,0,,And then, I just need something to\Nmake sure Shimamura doesn't get bored.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.30,0:04:24.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's not going to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.14,0:04:31.10,Default,,0,0,0,,If we can't think of anything to do,\NI guess we can just watch TV together.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.55,0:04:36.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe, just maybe...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.68,0:04:41.51,Default,,0,0,0,,The same thing will happen and hopefully,\NI won't run away again.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.68,0:04:53.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not going to run away!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.60,0:04:58.39,Default,,0,0,0,,G-Good morning...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.47,0:05:03.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You know...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.39,0:05:07.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh... You seem to have a lot of stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.05,0:05:13.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You do realize you're not moving, right?\NIt's a bit much.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.76,0:05:15.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.26,0:05:20.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Also, aren't you early? It's still 8 AM.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.64,0:05:23.22,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Sorry. Were you sleeping?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.22,0:05:25.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yup, you woke me up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.30,0:05:26.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.22,0:05:28.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh, it's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.55,0:05:33.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You're always so punctual, Adachi. That's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.72,0:05:38.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I was actually here at 7 AM,\Nbut I figured that was a bit too early.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.85,0:05:42.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't tell her I was just wandering\Naround on my bike for an hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.64,0:05:46.89,Default,,0,0,0,,That's probably the only\Nweird part of this, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.89,0:05:49.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.93,0:05:51.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.47,0:05:53.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-Thanks...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.47,0:06:02.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You remember my friend, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.85,0:06:08.22,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hi...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.22,0:06:11.55,Default,,0,0,0,,She's being a good girl today.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.55,0:06:17.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Is the room upstairs okay? Or well...\NThat's the only open room we have.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.35,0:06:21.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? Did you not want to go upstairs?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.72,0:06:23.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Not exactly...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.72,0:06:27.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess I won't be staying\Nin the same room as you...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.85,0:06:30.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You want to stay in the same room as me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.80,0:06:39.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm fine with it, but I don't think\Nmy little sister will like that. Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.80,0:06:48.14,Default,,0,0,0,,There was no way this was\Nall going to go as I planned.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.14,0:06:53.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not sure if Shimamura's okay\Nwith me staying in her room...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.26,0:06:57.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm fine with it, but I don't think\Nmy little sister will like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.80,0:07:01.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm fine with it... I'm fine with it...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.80,0:07:05.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Or maybe she is!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.97,0:07:08.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.39,0:07:11.01,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you want to do for breakfast?\NDid you already eat?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.01,0:07:14.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry. I came prepared.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.01,0:07:15.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Long Long Sticks"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.30,0:07:18.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey, hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.01,0:07:21.47,Default,,0,0,0,,What? My cooking's not good enough for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.47,0:07:25.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no. I'll have some. Thank you very much...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.64,0:07:27.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Dig in.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.64,0:07:32.14,Default,,0,0,0,,So, Adachi,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.14,0:07:35.76,Default,,0,0,0,,you probably actually go to school\Nunlike this daughter of mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.76,0:07:38.14,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.14,0:07:40.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Adachi's in the same boat.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.14,0:07:41.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.72,0:07:46.35,Default,,0,0,0,,She looks like a nice, quiet girl,\Nunlike my delinquent over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.35,0:07:48.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.68,0:07:53.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Shimamura's more of a good girl than I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.55,0:07:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Good girl...?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.64,0:08:01.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. So you must be older, Adachi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.22,0:08:05.26,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.22,0:08:20.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for the grub.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.30,0:08:23.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.80,0:08:28.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, are you mad?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.39,0:08:29.89,Default,,0,0,0,,About what?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.89,0:08:37.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, earlier? My mom's always like that,\Nso there's no point in getting mad.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.89,0:08:41.26,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's just how their relationship is.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.26,0:08:43.85,Default,,0,0,0,,More importantly, Adachi...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.85,0:08:46.68,Default,,0,0,0,,What should we do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.93,0:08:51.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder how long it's been\Nsince I was able to feel
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.30,0:08:53.85,Default,,0,0,0,,that days off were actually special?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.64,0:08:58.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Yesterday, the first day I stayed over,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.22,0:09:01.47,Default,,0,0,0,,really did end with nothing happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.47,0:09:07.72,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Well, I'll see you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.72,0:09:10.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Have a good day!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.60,0:09:13.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.35,0:09:18.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing special with Shimamura\Nactually happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.43,0:09:21.43,Default,,0,0,0,,We were just there together.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.43,0:09:24.43,Default,,0,0,0,,--Just being with her might\Njust be ideal to me, but...\N--Meat was really cheap\Nat the supermarket today.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.43,0:09:28.89,Default,,0,0,0,,--Just being with her might\Njust be ideal to me, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.89,0:09:30.30,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.85,0:09:37.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I'm going to do my best!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.05,0:09:46.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, you do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.35,0:09:48.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Shimamura laughed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.76,0:09:51.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Today might be a good day after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.97,0:09:55.97,Default,,0,0,0,,But then again,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.97,0:09:59.39,Default,,0,0,0,,it's not like absolutely\Nnothing happened yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.39,0:10:01.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Not exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.43,0:10:06.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Hogetsu, hurry up, and take a bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.72,0:10:09.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You go right to bed whenever you get full.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.30,0:10:12.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.93,0:10:15.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for the meal...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.85,0:10:21.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? You brought that, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.93,0:10:24.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Shimamura's room is on the first floor,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.51,0:10:27.72,Default,,0,0,0,,--You're too polite, Adachi.\NYou could've just used ours.\N--but she naturally came to my room.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.72,0:10:28.76,Default,,0,0,0,,--You're too polite, Adachi.\NYou could've just used ours.\N--That made me so happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.76,0:10:30.89,Default,,0,0,0,,--B-But I wanted to cause you\Nthe least amount of trouble.\N--That made me so happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.89,0:10:33.26,Default,,0,0,0,,--B-But I wanted to cause you\Nthe least amount of trouble.\N--I'm not exactly towards who,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.26,0:10:36.43,Default,,0,0,0,,but I felt superior towards them.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.43,0:10:41.14,Default,,0,0,0,,So, at that moment...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.14,0:10:44.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I got a little bold.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.60,0:10:49.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I... um, sit between your legs?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.39,0:10:52.18,Default,,0,0,0,,As long as you don't
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.18,0:10:54.89,Default,,0,0,0,,run away this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.55,0:10:58.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.43,0:11:01.26,Default,,0,0,0,,O-Okay, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.30,0:11:06.35,Default,,0,0,0,,D-Don't mind if I do...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.60,0:11:11.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not going to scooch closer?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.93,0:11:14.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure. Then, excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.35,0:11:18.10,Default,,0,0,0,,So soft... Eek.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.10,0:11:25.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-There's no reason to panic.\NShimamura's a girl, but so am I... yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.30,0:11:33.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Sh-Shimamura...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.68,0:11:41.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess she does fall asleep\Nright after eating...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.55,0:11:59.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What's up? Why do you have\Na change of clothes?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.89,0:12:01.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, a bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.89,0:12:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You want to take one first? That's rare.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.80,0:12:08.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's take one together.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.85,0:12:13.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Where'd that come from?\NI thought you said you're embarrassed to.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.22,0:12:16.43,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay sometimes... Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.43,0:12:18.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.97,0:12:20.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.68,0:12:22.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess I'm going...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.97,0:12:34.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Shimamura...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.60,0:12:36.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop daydreaming.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.01,0:12:37.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.85,0:12:43.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Ahem. Thanks for having me over...\Nor maybe I should say, "I'm home."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.80,0:12:45.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Adachi?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.68,0:12:47.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.14,0:12:50.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, well, welcome home.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.01,0:12:52.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I've returned...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.97,0:12:57.14,Default,,0,0,0,,My daughter's out right now.\NShe said something about shopping.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.14,0:12:59.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.01,0:13:01.39,Default,,0,0,0,,She should be back soon, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.39,0:13:03.64,Default,,0,0,0,,She can be pretty lazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.10,0:13:09.26,Default,,0,0,0,,She's always been a sleepyhead\Never since she was little.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.26,0:13:12.93,Default,,0,0,0,,She really does sleep a lot like a koala.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.72,0:13:17.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah. How's she doing at school?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.35,0:13:21.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Is she actually going to class?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.14,0:13:22.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.55,0:13:27.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that's good. She tends to be lazy,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.26,0:13:29.26,Default,,0,0,0,,so it must be hard to get her to do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.26,0:13:33.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Not at all. Actually, it's the opposite.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.35,0:13:34.39,Default,,0,0,0,,The opposite?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.39,0:13:39.26,Default,,0,0,0,,She always leads... Is that the right word?\NShe always leads me around.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.26,0:13:41.43,Default,,0,0,0,,That's actually surprising.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.43,0:13:45.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm home. Oh, welcome back, Adachi.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.60,0:13:47.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm back.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.01,0:13:49.01,Default,,0,0,0,,WB.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.01,0:13:51.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I see you're both enjoying some {\i1}dango{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.26,0:13:53.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You didn't say anything weird to her, did you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.47,0:14:00.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess upstairs works.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.35,0:14:04.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that I look at it,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.35,0:14:08.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I think "lead" really was the right term.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.26,0:14:14.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I pretty much follow Shimamura\Naround like her little puppy dog.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.14,0:14:16.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, sit there.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.05,0:14:18.47,Default,,0,0,0,,O-Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.47,0:14:22.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, lower your head and bend down a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.22,0:14:24.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? L-Like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.97,0:14:27.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay just like that for a sec.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.89,0:14:35.85,Default,,0,0,0,,And then, we go like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.68,0:14:42.30,Default,,0,0,0,,And there we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.35,0:14:46.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Yup. Now you have the same hairstyle as me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.60,0:14:53.01,Default,,0,0,0,,A moment, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.01,0:14:53.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.47,0:14:57.60,Default,,0,0,0,,My hair color's starting to match yours,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.60,0:15:01.05,Default,,0,0,0,,so I figured we'd end up looking a lot alike.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.10,0:15:06.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see... Hm.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.30,0:15:12.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe we don't look that much alike.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.35,0:15:15.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah. You can have that hairclip.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.72,0:15:17.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.64,0:15:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,But that...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.80,0:15:21.30,Default,,0,0,0,,But that...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.26,0:15:26.22,Default,,0,0,0,,But that means we're matching!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.10,0:15:41.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I... Sh-Shimamura, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.64,0:15:47.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I... wuv...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.55,0:15:51.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You look wuvly!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.93,0:15:55.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Wuvly, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.60,0:15:58.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You look lovely, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.89,0:16:03.30,Default,,0,0,0,,We did this before, by the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.30,0:16:04.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.64,0:16:13.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You're so funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.55,0:16:17.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's stretch out those cheeks.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.18,0:16:19.60,Default,,0,0,0,,L-Let's not.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.01,0:16:22.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Shimamura.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.97,0:16:27.68,Default,,0,0,0,,So today...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.93,0:16:34.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want to sleep together today?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.10,0:16:36.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.72,0:16:42.72,Default,,0,0,0,,She didn't even hesitate. Then actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.72,0:16:47.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I should've suggested this yesterday, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.39,0:16:53.05,Default,,0,0,0,,But will it be okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.05,0:16:55.14,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.14,0:16:58.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Your sister sleeping on her own.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.68,0:17:00.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.64,0:17:04.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Because she has a friend\Nsleeping over today, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.89,0:17:08.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Little?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.30,0:17:13.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I shall teach you about the universe, Little.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.64,0:17:15.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-The universe?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.93,0:17:17.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.68,0:17:22.89,Default,,0,0,0,,First, my kind tends to live\Nan average of 800 million years,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.89,0:17:26.97,Default,,0,0,0,,so I belong to species\Nthat lives for a much longer time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.97,0:17:28.55,Default,,0,0,0,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.55,0:17:30.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, I'm turning off the lights.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.10,0:17:31.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.55,0:17:36.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Night.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.60,0:18:23.72,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.97,0:18:28.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I was just wondering if you\Nwere really asleep...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.72,0:18:32.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, yeah. I'm in my futon.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.10,0:18:34.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.47,0:18:37.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to grow more\Ndistant with Shimamura.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.93,0:18:42.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Three, two, one. My courage\Nis trying to tell me to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.60,0:18:46.55,Default,,0,0,0,,My courage is taking the initiative,\Nand kicking me in the ass.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.55,0:18:56.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You fell like a bug.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.35,0:19:01.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Want to sleep together?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.93,0:19:06.93,Default,,0,0,0,,The universe... The universe...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.72,0:19:12.22,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you like your Big Sis's shoulder pillow?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.22,0:19:13.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.26,0:19:14.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.39,0:19:16.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel like I'm going to cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.68,0:19:21.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Your hair's still a bit wet.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.47,0:19:28.93,Default,,0,0,0,,There's something about that warmth\Nyou feel when it's wet that feels nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.93,0:19:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I have my arm back now?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.80,0:19:33.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.14,0:19:35.43,Default,,0,0,0,,How much longer?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.43,0:19:38.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Until I fall asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.35,0:19:40.43,Default,,0,0,0,,What am I ever going to do with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.43,0:19:42.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah. We're changing desks tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.97,0:19:45.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? We are?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.39,0:19:49.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you didn't know\Nbecause you skipped class.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.10,0:19:53.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Adachi?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.43,0:19:57.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It'd be great if we could sit this close.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.26,0:20:02.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Er, I'm sure there'd be a few\Nproblems if we sat this close...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.72,0:20:06.89,Default,,0,0,0,,What will be, will be.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.68,0:20:17.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's eat lunch together tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.35,0:20:22.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, of course. So relax, and go to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.72,0:20:28.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Adachi... Goodnight.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.51,0:20:31.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Goodnight.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.89,0:20:45.10,Default,,0,0,0,,We're heading out.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.10,0:20:46.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold your horses.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.39,0:20:51.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Take these with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.68,0:20:53.26,Default,,0,0,0,,What are these?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.26,0:20:56.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't you tell?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.10,0:20:59.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Packed lunches are making a comeback!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.18,0:21:00.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, why though?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.76,0:21:02.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh, why are you such a pain?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.97,0:21:12.55,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, I think this is the first time\Nwe've gone to school together.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.55,0:21:14.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.35,0:21:30.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Please let me sit near Shimamura.\NPlease let me sit near Shimamura.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.60,0:21:34.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Please let me sit near Shimamura...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.89,0:21:37.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Please let me...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.60,0:21:43.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder how much praying\Nactually helps in real life.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.93,0:21:47.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Adachi, eyes up front.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.43,0:21:53.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess finding that out is half the fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.47,0:22:01.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, this is sorta plain.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.18,0:22:07.72,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not like we got that much closer,\Nand we didn't move that much away.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.76,0:22:10.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Delinquent" "Adachi"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.60,0:22:13.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Delinquent" "Adachi"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.60,0:22:13.51,Default,,0,0,0,,And before I knew it, it had already been\Na month since we became second-years.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.51,0:22:17.01,Default,,0,0,0,,And before I knew it, it had already been\Na month since we became second-years.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.01,0:22:21.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll only have one more April in high school.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.76,0:22:29.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Then it'll be May, then June...\NThe time we have isn't infinite.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.85,0:22:33.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Yummy!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.60,0:22:37.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Someday... Yes, someday,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.55,0:22:40.10,Default,,0,0,0,,even if I can't imagine it clearly,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.10,0:22:44.60,Default,,0,0,0,,the future is inevitable. A world\Nwhere there'll be no spring breaks.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.60,0:22:49.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Or perhaps, a future where\Nthere's no one next to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.01,0:22:50.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be walking down
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.55,0:22:56.97,Default,,0,0,0,,a spring path while looking up at the\Ncherry blossoms whether I want to or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.93,0:23:02.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Shimamura!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.05,0:23:10.55,Default,,0,0,0,,And until then,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.55,0:23:15.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess I'll settle for the cherry blossom\Nthat's right in front of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.26,0:23:17.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't mind it at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.22,0:23:24.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the end of April. There aren't\Nany more cherry blossoms anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.26,0:23:29.18,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's why... I'll need Adachi\Nto be my cherry blossom.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.60,0:23:41.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Her profile will always...
